{"tid":2274343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲男生藏伸縮棍鐳射筆罪成　法庭索取報告後判刑","createTime":"2020-11-06T11:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T11:20:51.000Z","uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"853d6b7a05050732e3bb14d05cd9e175f6e74abe","tid":2274343,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"去年11月9日有市民在金鐘添馬公園聚集，悼念逝世科大學生周梓樂。一名19歲男學生當晚被人搜出伸縮棍及未裝上電池的鐳射筆，早前被裁定管有攻擊性武器罪成，案件原定今日判刑，不過裁判官決定再索取更生中心及青少年罪犯評估專案小組報告，被告要繼續還押至本月20日。辯方指出，懲教報告認為被告合作，被告形容事件魯莽，後悔出席集會又或後悔帶同有關物品到集會，不過，裁判官鄭紀航表示，不相信被告當晚是會與母親交收有關物品，不相信被告有悔意。辯方希望法庭判刑時考慮被告年紀輕、無案底以及有意繼續海外升學等因素，被捕後亦已作很多轉變，雖然報告指被告適合進入教導所，但認為長時間還押教導所是不合比例，向法庭提出以14日囚禁處理。裁判官表示，會判處羈押式刑期，但不認為14日判期合適，要求再索取兩份報告。<br />\n<br />\n2020-11-06 15:42:01"},{"pid":"06d8eea29ba8c05aa8d3e1913ee4b2cb77568c8a","tid":2274343,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"又一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535cd55630a59917a2631c158c51d0f0b1d28693","tid":2274343,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06d8eea29ba8c05aa8d3e1913ee4b2cb77568c8a","tid":2274343,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"又一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c297d75805ab02a00fab5e5326e8778af2cf9550","tid":2274343,"uid":135276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:20:51.000Z","msg":"未裝電柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}